You are creating an app that helps the user build their CV on the front end.

The cv will have sections such as -

--Personal Profile
In this section the person will be able to display their -
    first name, middle name and last name as their full name
    their email
    their phone
    their location
    their photo of themeselves
All of these will be optional except for their first name and last name

--Work experience
This section will display where they've worked in descending date order. Each experience will be able to display -
    experience title
    experience start date
    experience end date
    description
    key responsibilities - these will be catagories that they can create and edit within eac of with they can create a list of responsibilities
Education
Projects
Skills
Certifications
Professional qualification equivilance
Professional memberships
Intersts and activities



Each section will then come together to make the full cv which the user will be able to display as a website or print out as a pdf.
